{"tid":756301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬老翁港鐵站偷《成報》被捕","createTime":"2018-07-26T02:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T10:25:19.000Z","uid":122,"like":197,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2fcc996b15c9e0c02ecdfc47a6bc8ecd7db4fe29","tid":756301,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"港鐵南昌站發生偷竊案。今晨6時許，一名七旬老翁在港鐵南昌站一間尚未營業的便利店外，順手牽羊拿取未曾疊報的《成報》的其中一張報紙。剛將報紙送到便利店的37歲黃姐送報工人見狀阻止，但被老翁的雨傘打中手臂。警方接報到場，將該名76歲徐姓老翁，以盜竊及襲擊拘捕。"},{"pid":"b8e0d2c32991b5d2eb5e9355a1fadafc344a07d1","tid":756301,"uid":96941,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"報紙都要偷 屌你老味ON鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e59d6ee833685bdee30330dc97741f978c50d50","tid":756301,"uid":15182,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"廢老 +1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff067bcee22a8585070fdb688236020ad47035c","tid":756301,"uid":137703,"like":142,"dislike":0,"score":142,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c582089fccd49aa471beeb5023b2a3c84a87238a","tid":756301,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"我唔小心咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82e21f238d7c80cd38979ef2b0de6ad8981d72d","tid":756301,"uid":74171,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"eff067bcee22a8585070fdb688236020ad47035c","tid":756301,"uid":137703,"like":142,"dislike":0,"score":142,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"死廢青，拎份報紙都唔得<br />\n係咪唔拎得，係咪唔拎得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18cd50ed4b62a260fcbf2c